{"tid":1588270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「公職人員行為失當罪」＋「公民拘捕權」可以點運用？（法律知識討論）","createTime":"2019-09-22T17:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:54:41.000Z","uid":319163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aed60b3207072e3dd8ff5043c47d2acb550b901c","tid":1588270,"uid":319163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">P牌虛心求教，拋磚引玉，不喜請大大力狠挿。<br />\n<br />\n如果於衝突現場目擊有公職人員違法，以懷疑干犯「公職人員行為失當罪」為原因行使公民拘捕權制服該公職人員，是否可行？（於現場以大聲公宣讀懷疑該公職人員所干犯的罪行並全程拍片記錄，並於制服公職人員時使用合適武力。）<br />\n<br />\n至少當見義勇為的市民被指控「襲警」時，可用上述理據抗辯？</span>"},{"pid":"7edef689949d79143565d39a9f241243b5b70e84","tid":1588270,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"19c0b9f700937294f04cd52c83cc6f3a06a3c2b9","tid":1588270,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1:你制服到佢先<br />\n2:你制服到佢再唔比佢call馬先<br />\n3:你制服到佢佢call馬你唔比人因為襲警而拉先"}]}